OL,6,FVictims of a paedophile applauded a
OL,7,Fjudge and burst into tears, as their
OL,8,Fabuser was jailed for 28 years for the
OL,9,Frape and sexual abuse of seven girls.
OL,11,FFormer ice hockey player and TV extra
OL,12,FPhilip Hamer had a "wholly distorted
OL,13,Fview of children as sexual objects,"
OL,14,FManchester Crown Court was told.
OL,16,FHamer, from Birchfield Drive, Worsley
OL,17,Fin Greater Manchester, targeted girls
OL,18,Fin their early to mid-teens via social
OL,19,Fmedia.
