OL,6,FHe was 20 when he groomed his first
OL,7,Fvictim, who was 14, back in 2010 and
OL,8,Fwent on to groom an 11-year-old, when
OL,9,Fhe was aged 27.
OL,11,FThe now 34-year-old admitted 20
OL,12,Foffences but denied others, claiming
OL,13,Fone victim was "wanton" and "sexually
OL,14,Fexperienced" but a jury convicted him
OL,15,Fof a further 21 offences after a trial.
