OL,6,FJailing him for 28 years, with an
OL,7,Fextended licence period of eight
OL,8,Fyears, Judge Sarah Johnston told the
OL,9,Fdefendant: "These were no
OL,10,Frelationships ` you manipulated and
OL,11,Fgroomed these young girls,
OL,12,Finexperienced and impressionable as
OL,13,Fthey were, in a way that was
OL,14,Fcontrolling and coercive.
OL,16,F"Your offending is both opportunistic
OL,17,Fand actively seeking out,
OL,18,Fmanipulating, grooming, exploiting and
OL,19,Fthe abuse of female children, mostly
OL,20,Fteens but including a child as young
